data.oai_dc:dc: This is a Kuparuk River rock-scrubbing. The insects are cinygmula. The file simply lists thelength of each insect measured, as well as when and where along theriver it was captured. Only the actual measurements of the insectsare listed, for example, if there wasn't a particular insect foundfrom a replicate at a station, then that station isn't listed either.This file is for cinygmula.
